name: Business first, pleasure afterwards
description:
The red flame of the flag rising above the common proletariat. Only the great Vova continued to speak of the future with gleaming eyes. 

In principle, what is wrong? When we look at the past, we do not endure the outcome, diligently writing it down in a notebook. We only talk about and confirm what our eyes haven't seen. 

We did not attend at that time. It is not for us to pass judgment.
